r might actually help — it reframes the company before the story hardens. I'd want outside M&A counsel on this before you commit either direction. Can we get them on a call today?"" CEO Ajay messaged me privately: ""Set it up. 4 PM if possible."" CEO Ajay messaged me privately: ""Outside counsel call done. Their advice: hold the proactive statement until Thursday at the earliest — they want to review it for disclosure implications given the Project context. We hold. Tell the team. And tell PR the statement is good — it's just not today.""",Damage control; ResidentIQ attacks; 'No Plan B' speech,"Pre-crisis Day 12 (2046-06-01, Friday). Damage control mode. PR team issues careful non-denial of SaltWind piece. ResidentIQ publicly posts 'privacy-first is not a feature, it's the floor' — gets 4,200 retweets. In Shadow: 'We need this merger to close before this gets any worse.' Ajay sends evening DM: 'No Plan B.'"
